      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed (4.2 M, 12.1 M, 34.7 M cells). GCI on normalised hemolysis index is 3.8% between medium and fine meshes. Medium mesh selected for production runs as cost-accuracy optimum."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
